description: Shifts left under inverse Euler transform.
links: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
maple: with(numtheory): ietr:= proc(p) local a, c; c:= proc(n) option remember; local j; n*p(n)-add(c(j)*p(n-j), j=1..n-1) end; a:=proc(n) option remember; local d; `if`(n=0, 1, add (mobius (n/d)*c(d), d=divisors(n))/n) end end: aa:= ietr('a'): a:= n-> `if`(n<=1,1, aa(n-1)): seq (a(n), n=1..48);  # _Alois P. Heinz_, Sep 08 2008
author: _Christian G. Bower_, Jan 04 1999
